refsection.programlisting:
r = hendryericsson();statfore(r, '1985q1', '1989q3 ')
// Example shows the static forecast made on period 1985q1 to 1989q3 with Hendry and Ericsson preferred specification.
r2=ols(r('y'),r('x'));statfore(r2,[0.02 0.01 0.03 0.015 1])
// Example shows a static forecast made with the same model, but estimated now with the corresponding vectors (r('y') and r('x')), and with exogenous values equal to [0.02 0.01 0.03 0.015 1].
